<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">أبو ثور:</span> انظر ج‍ ١ ص ٢٥٢<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">الثورى:</span> انظر ج‍ ١ ص ٢٥٢<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
